00291 static int rna_member_cmp(const char *name, const char *oname)
00292 {
00293     int a = 0;
00294     
00295     /* compare without pointer or array part */
00296     while (name[0] =='*')
00297         name++;
00298     while (oname[0] =='*')
00299         oname++;
00300     
00301     while (1) {
00302         if (name[a] =='[' && oname[a] == 0) return 1;
00303         if (name[a] =='[' && oname[a] =='[') return 1;
00304         if (name[a] == 0) break;
00305         if (name[a] != oname[a]) return 0;
00306         a++;
00307     }
00308     if (name[a] == 0 && oname[a] == '.') return 2;
00309     if (name[a] == 0 && oname[a] == '-' && oname[a+1] == '>') return 3;
00310 
00311     return (name[a] == oname[a]);
00312 }

00375 static int rna_validate_identifier(const char *identifier, char *error, int property)
00376 {
00377     int a = 0;
00378     
00379     /*  list from http://docs.python.org/py3k/reference/lexical_analysis.html#keywords */
00380     static const char *kwlist[] = {
00381         /* "False", "None", "True", */
00382         "and", "as", "assert", "break",
00383         "class", "continue", "def", "del", "elif", "else", "except",
00384         "finally", "for", "from", "global", "if", "import", "in",
00385         "is", "lambda", "nonlocal", "not", "or", "pass", "raise",
00386         "return", "try", "while", "with", "yield", NULL
00387     };
00388     
00389     
00390     if (!isalpha(identifier[0])) {
00391         strcpy(error, "first character failed isalpha() check");
00392         return 0;
00393     }
00394     
00395     for (a = 0; identifier[a]; a++) {
00396         if (DefRNA.preprocess && property) {
00397             if (isalpha(identifier[a]) && isupper(identifier[a])) {
00398                 strcpy(error, "property names must contain lower case characters only");
00399                 return 0;
00400             }
00401         }
00402         
00403         if (identifier[a] =='_') {
00404             continue;
00405         }
00406 
00407         if (identifier[a] ==' ') {
00408             strcpy(error, "spaces are not okay in identifier names");
00409             return 0;
00410         }
00411 
00412         if (isalnum(identifier[a]) == 0) {
00413             strcpy(error, "one of the characters failed an isalnum() check and is not an underscore");
00414             return 0;
00415         }
00416     }
00417     
00418     for (a = 0; kwlist[a]; a++) {
00419         if (strcmp(identifier, kwlist[a]) == 0) {
00420             strcpy(error, "this keyword is reserved by python");
00421             return 0;
00422         }
00423     }
00424 
00425     if (property) {
00426         static const char *kwlist_prop[] = {
00427             /* not keywords but reserved all the same because py uses */
00428             "keys", "values", "items", "get",
00429             NULL
00430         };
00431 
00432         for (a = 0; kwlist_prop[a]; a++) {
00433             if (strcmp(identifier, kwlist_prop[a]) == 0) {
00434                 strcpy(error, "this keyword is reserved by python");
00435                 return 0;
00436             }
00437         }
00438     }
00439     
00440     return 1;
00441 }

00670     /* in preprocess, try to find sdna */
00671     if (DefRNA.preprocess)
00672         RNA_def_struct_sdna(srna, srna->identifier);
00673     else
00674         srna->flag |= STRUCT_RUNTIME;
00675 
00676     if (srnafrom) {
00677         srna->nameproperty = srnafrom->nameproperty;
00678         srna->iteratorproperty = srnafrom->iteratorproperty;
00679     }
00680     else {
00681         /* define some builtin properties */
00682         prop = RNA_def_property(&srna->cont, "rna_properties", PROP_COLLECTION, PROP_NONE);
00683         RNA_def_property_flag(prop, PROP_BUILTIN);
00684         RNA_def_property_ui_text(prop, "Properties", "RNA property collection");
00685 
00686         if (DefRNA.preprocess) {
00687             RNA_def_property_struct_type(prop, "Property");
00688             RNA_def_property_collection_funcs(prop, "rna_builtin_properties_begin", "rna_builtin_properties_next",
00689                                               "rna_iterator_listbase_end", "rna_builtin_properties_get", NULL, NULL,
00690                                               "rna_builtin_properties_lookup_string", NULL);
00691         }
00692         else {
00693 #ifdef RNA_RUNTIME
00694             CollectionPropertyRNA *cprop = (CollectionPropertyRNA*)prop;
00695             cprop->begin = rna_builtin_properties_begin;
00696             cprop->next = rna_builtin_properties_next;
00697             cprop->get = rna_builtin_properties_get;
00698             cprop->item_type = &RNA_Property;
00699 #endif
00700         }
00701 
00702         prop = RNA_def_property(&srna->cont, "rna_type", PROP_POINTER, PROP_NONE);
00703         RNA_def_property_flag(prop, PROP_HIDDEN);
00704         RNA_def_property_ui_text(prop, "RNA", "RNA type definition");
00705 
00706         if (DefRNA.preprocess) {
00707             RNA_def_property_struct_type(prop, "Struct");
00708             RNA_def_property_pointer_funcs(prop, "rna_builtin_type_get", NULL, NULL, NULL);
00709         }
00710         else {
00711 #ifdef RNA_RUNTIME
00712             PointerPropertyRNA *pprop = (PointerPropertyRNA*)prop;
00713             pprop->get = rna_builtin_type_get;
00714             pprop->type = &RNA_Struct;

00716         }
00717     }
00718 
00719     return srna;
00720 }

00880 
00881 PropertyRNA *RNA_def_property(StructOrFunctionRNA *cont_, const char *identifier, int type, int subtype)
00882 {
00883     /*StructRNA *srna= DefRNA.laststruct;*/ /* invalid for python defined props */
00884     ContainerRNA *cont = cont_;
00885     ContainerDefRNA *dcont;
00886     PropertyDefRNA *dprop = NULL;
00887     PropertyRNA *prop;
00888 
00889     if (DefRNA.preprocess) {
00890         char error[512];
00891         
00892         if (rna_validate_identifier(identifier, error, 1) == 0) {
00893             fprintf(stderr, "%s: property identifier \"%s.%s\" - %s\n", __func__,
00894                     CONTAINER_RNA_ID(cont), identifier, error);
00895             DefRNA.error = 1;
00896         }
00897         
00898         dcont = rna_find_container_def(cont);
00899 
00900         /* XXX - toto, detect supertype collisions */
00901         if (rna_findlink(&dcont->properties, identifier)) {
00902             fprintf(stderr, "%s: duplicate identifier \"%s.%s\"\n", __func__, CONTAINER_RNA_ID(cont), identifier);
00903             DefRNA.error = 1;
00904         }
00905 
00906         dprop = MEM_callocN(sizeof(PropertyDefRNA), "PropertyDefRNA");
00907         rna_addtail(&dcont->properties, dprop);
00908     }
00909 
00910     prop = MEM_callocN(rna_property_type_sizeof(type), "PropertyRNA");
00911 
00912     switch (type) {
00913         case PROP_BOOLEAN:
00914             if (DefRNA.preprocess) {
00915                 if ((subtype & ~(PROP_LAYER_MEMBER)) != PROP_NONE) {
00916                     fprintf(stderr, "%s: subtype does not apply to 'PROP_BOOLEAN' \"%s.%s\"\n", __func__,
00917                             CONTAINER_RNA_ID(cont), identifier);
00918                     DefRNA.error = 1;
00919                 }
00920             }
00921             break;
00922         case PROP_INT: {
00923             IntPropertyRNA *iprop = (IntPropertyRNA*)prop;
00924 
00925             iprop->hardmin = (subtype == PROP_UNSIGNED)? 0: INT_MIN;
00926             iprop->hardmax = INT_MAX;
00927 
00928             iprop->softmin = (subtype == PROP_UNSIGNED)? 0: -10000; /* rather arbitrary .. */
00929             iprop->softmax = 10000;
00930             iprop->step = 1;
00931             break;
00932         }
00933         case PROP_FLOAT: {
00934             FloatPropertyRNA *fprop = (FloatPropertyRNA*)prop;
00935 
00936             fprop->hardmin = (subtype == PROP_UNSIGNED)? 0.0f: -FLT_MAX;
00937             fprop->hardmax = FLT_MAX;
00938 
00939             if (ELEM(subtype, PROP_COLOR, PROP_COLOR_GAMMA)) {
00940                 fprop->softmin = 0.0f;
00941                 fprop->softmax = 1.0f;
00942             }
00943             else if (subtype == PROP_FACTOR) {
00944                 fprop->softmin = fprop->hardmin = 0.0f;
00945                 fprop->softmax = fprop->hardmax = 1.0f;
00946             }
00947             else {
00948                 fprop->softmin = (subtype == PROP_UNSIGNED)? 0.0f: -10000.0f; /* rather arbitrary .. */
00949                 fprop->softmax = 10000.0f;
00950             }
00951             fprop->step = 10;
00952             fprop->precision = 3;
00953             break;
00954         }
00955         case PROP_STRING: {
00956             StringPropertyRNA *sprop = (StringPropertyRNA*)prop;
00957 
00958             sprop->defaultvalue = "";
00959             break;
00960         }
00961         case PROP_ENUM:
00962         case PROP_POINTER:
00963         case PROP_COLLECTION:
00964             break;
00965         default:
00966             fprintf(stderr, "%s: \"%s.%s\", invalid property type.\n", __func__, CONTAINER_RNA_ID(cont), identifier);
00967             DefRNA.error = 1;
00968             return NULL;
00969     }
00970 
00971     if (DefRNA.preprocess) {
00972         dprop->cont = cont;
00973         dprop->prop = prop;
00974     }
00975 
00976     prop->magic = RNA_MAGIC;
00977     prop->identifier = identifier;
00978     prop->type = type;
00979     prop->subtype = subtype;
00980     prop->name = identifier;
00981     prop->description = "";
00982     /* a priori not raw editable */
00983     prop->rawtype = -1;
00984 
00985     if (type != PROP_COLLECTION && type != PROP_POINTER) {
00986         prop->flag = PROP_EDITABLE;
00987     
00988         if (type != PROP_STRING)
00989             prop->flag |= PROP_ANIMATABLE;
00990     }
00991 
00992     if (type == PROP_STRING) {
00993         /* used so generated 'get/length/set' functions skip a NULL check
00994          * in some cases we want it */
00995         RNA_def_property_flag(prop, PROP_NEVER_NULL);
00996     }
00997 
00998     if (DefRNA.preprocess) {
00999         switch (type) {
01000             case PROP_BOOLEAN:
01001                 DefRNA.silent = 1;
01002                 RNA_def_property_boolean_sdna(prop, NULL, identifier, 0);
01003                 DefRNA.silent = 0;
01004                 break;
01005             case PROP_INT: {
01006                 DefRNA.silent = 1;
01007                 RNA_def_property_int_sdna(prop, NULL, identifier);
01008                 DefRNA.silent = 0;
01009                 break;
01010             }
01011             case PROP_FLOAT: {
01012                 DefRNA.silent = 1;
01013                 RNA_def_property_float_sdna(prop, NULL, identifier);
01014                 DefRNA.silent = 0;
01015                 break;
01016             }
01017             case PROP_STRING: {
01018                 DefRNA.silent = 1;
01019                 RNA_def_property_string_sdna(prop, NULL, identifier);
01020                 DefRNA.silent = 0;
01021                 break;
01022             }
01023             case PROP_ENUM:
01024                 DefRNA.silent = 1;
01025                 RNA_def_property_enum_sdna(prop, NULL, identifier);
01026                 DefRNA.silent = 0;
01027                 break;
01028             case PROP_POINTER:
01029                 DefRNA.silent = 1;
01030                 RNA_def_property_pointer_sdna(prop, NULL, identifier);
01031                 DefRNA.silent = 0;
01032                 break;
01033             case PROP_COLLECTION:
01034                 DefRNA.silent = 1;
01035                 RNA_def_property_collection_sdna(prop, NULL, identifier, NULL);
01036                 DefRNA.silent = 0;
01037                 break;
01038         }
01039     }
01040     else {
01041         prop->flag |= PROP_IDPROPERTY|PROP_RUNTIME;
01042 #ifdef RNA_RUNTIME
01043         if (cont->prophash)
01044             BLI_ghash_insert(cont->prophash, (void*)prop->identifier, prop);
01045 #endif
01046     }
01047 
01048     rna_addtail(&cont->properties, prop);
01049 
01050     return prop;
01051 }

01068 void RNA_def_property_array(PropertyRNA *prop, int length)
01069 {
01070     StructRNA *srna = DefRNA.laststruct;
01071 
01072     if (length<0) {
01073         fprintf(stderr, "%s: \"%s.%s\", array length must be zero of greater.\n", __func__,
01074                 srna->identifier, prop->identifier);
01075         DefRNA.error = 1;
01076         return;
01077     }
01078 
01079     if (length>RNA_MAX_ARRAY_LENGTH) {
01080         fprintf(stderr, "%s: \"%s.%s\", array length must be smaller than %d.\n", __func__,
01081                 srna->identifier, prop->identifier, RNA_MAX_ARRAY_LENGTH);
01082         DefRNA.error = 1;
01083         return;
01084     }
01085 
01086     if (prop->arraydimension > 1) {
01087         fprintf(stderr, "%s: \"%s.%s\", array dimensions has been set to %u but would be overwritten as 1.\n",
01088                 __func__, srna->identifier, prop->identifier, prop->arraydimension);
01089         DefRNA.error = 1;
01090         return;
01091     }
01092 
01093     switch (prop->type) {
01094         case PROP_BOOLEAN:
01095         case PROP_INT:
01096         case PROP_FLOAT:
01097             prop->arraylength[0] = length;
01098             prop->totarraylength = length;
01099             prop->arraydimension = 1;
01100             break;
01101         default:
01102             fprintf(stderr, "%s: \"%s.%s\", only boolean/int/float can be array.\n",
01103                     __func__, srna->identifier, prop->identifier);
01104             DefRNA.error = 1;
01105             break;
01106     }
01107 }

01109 void RNA_def_property_multi_array(PropertyRNA *prop, int dimension, const int length[])
01110 {

01114     if (dimension < 1 || dimension > RNA_MAX_ARRAY_DIMENSION) {

01116                 __func__, srna->identifier, prop->identifier, RNA_MAX_ARRAY_DIMENSION);
01117         DefRNA.error = 1;
01118         return;
01119     }
01120 
01121     switch (prop->type) {

01123         case PROP_INT:
01124         case PROP_FLOAT:
01125             break;
01126         default:
01127             fprintf(stderr, "%s: \"%s.%s\", only boolean/int/float can be array.\n",

01140         for (i = 1; i<dimension; i++)
01141             prop->totarraylength *= length[i];
01142     }
01143     else
01144         memset(prop->arraylength, 0, sizeof(prop->arraylength));
01145 
01146     /* TODO make sure arraylength values are sane  */
01147 }

01452 void RNA_def_property_enum_default(PropertyRNA *prop, int value)
01453 {
01454     StructRNA *srna = DefRNA.laststruct;
01455     int i, defaultfound = 0;
01456 
01457     switch (prop->type) {
01458         case PROP_ENUM: {
01459             EnumPropertyRNA *eprop = (EnumPropertyRNA*)prop;
01460             eprop->defaultvalue = value;
01461 
01462             if (prop->flag & PROP_ENUM_FLAG) {
01463                 /* check all bits are accounted for */
01464                 int totflag = 0;
01465                 for (i = 0; i<eprop->totitem; i++) {
01466                     if (eprop->item[i].identifier[0]) {
01467                         totflag |= eprop->item[i].value;
01468                     }
01469                 }
01470 
01471                 if (eprop->defaultvalue & ~totflag) {
01472                     fprintf(stderr, "%s: \"%s.%s\", default includes unused bits (%d).\n",
01473                             __func__, srna->identifier, prop->identifier, eprop->defaultvalue & ~totflag);
01474                     DefRNA.error = 1;
01475                 }
01476             }
01477             else {
01478                 for (i = 0; i<eprop->totitem; i++) {
01479                     if (eprop->item[i].identifier[0] && eprop->item[i].value == eprop->defaultvalue)
01480                         defaultfound = 1;
01481                 }
01482 
01483                 if (!defaultfound && eprop->totitem) {
01484                     if (value == 0) {
01485                         eprop->defaultvalue = eprop->item[0].value;
01486                     }
01487                     else {
01488                         fprintf(stderr, "%s: \"%s.%s\", default is not in items.\n",
01489                                 __func__, srna->identifier, prop->identifier);
01490                         DefRNA.error = 1;
01491                     }
01492                 }
01493             }
01494 
01495             break;
01496         }
01497         default:
01498             fprintf(stderr, "%s: \"%s.%s\", type is not enum.\n", __func__, srna->identifier, prop->identifier);
01499             DefRNA.error = 1;
01500             break;
01501     }
01502 }

01505 
01506 static PropertyDefRNA *rna_def_property_sdna(PropertyRNA *prop, const char *structname, const char *propname)
01507 {
01508     DNAStructMember smember;
01509     StructDefRNA *ds;
01510     PropertyDefRNA *dp;
01511 
01512     dp = rna_find_struct_property_def(DefRNA.laststruct, prop);
01513     if (dp == NULL) return NULL;
01514 
01515     ds = rna_find_struct_def((StructRNA*)dp->cont);
01516 
01517     if (!structname)
01518         structname = ds->dnaname;
01519     if (!propname)
01520         propname = prop->identifier;
01521 
01522     if (!rna_find_sdna_member(DefRNA.sdna, structname, propname, &smember)) {
01523         if (DefRNA.silent) {
01524             return NULL;
01525         }
01526         else if (!DefRNA.verify) {
01527             /* some basic values to survive even with sdna info */
01528             dp->dnastructname = structname;
01529             dp->dnaname = propname;
01530             if (prop->type == PROP_BOOLEAN)
01531                 dp->dnaarraylength = 1;
01532             if (prop->type == PROP_POINTER)
01533                 dp->dnapointerlevel = 1;
01534             return dp;
01535         }
01536         else {
01537             fprintf(stderr, "%s: \"%s.%s\" (identifier \"%s\") not found.\n",
01538                     __func__, structname, propname, prop->identifier);
01539             DefRNA.error = 1;
01540             return NULL;
01541         }
01542     }
01543 
01544     if (smember.arraylength > 1) {
01545         prop->arraylength[0] = smember.arraylength;
01546         prop->totarraylength = smember.arraylength;
01547         prop->arraydimension = 1;
01548     }
01549     else {
01550         prop->arraydimension = 0;
01551         prop->totarraylength = 0;
01552     }
01553     
01554     dp->dnastructname = structname;
01555     dp->dnastructfromname = ds->dnafromname;
01556     dp->dnastructfromprop = ds->dnafromprop;
01557     dp->dnaname = propname;
01558     dp->dnatype = smember.type;
01559     dp->dnaarraylength = smember.arraylength;
01560     dp->dnapointerlevel = smember.pointerlevel;
01561 
01562     return dp;
01563 }

01652             iprop->softmin = -10000; /* rather arbitrary .. */
01653             iprop->softmax = 10000;

01656         if (prop->subtype == PROP_UNSIGNED || prop->subtype == PROP_PERCENTAGE || prop->subtype == PROP_FACTOR)

02697 int rna_parameter_size(PropertyRNA *parm)
02698 {
02699     PropertyType ptype = parm->type;
02700     int len = parm->totarraylength; /* only supports fixed length at the moment */
02701 
02702     if (len > 0) {
02703         /* XXX in other parts is mentioned that strings can be dynamic as well */
02704         if (parm->flag & PROP_DYNAMIC)
02705             return sizeof(void *);
02706 
02707         switch (ptype) {
02708             case PROP_BOOLEAN:
02709             case PROP_INT:
02710                 return sizeof(int)*len;
02711             case PROP_FLOAT:
02712                 return sizeof(float)*len;
02713             default:
02714                 break;
02715         }
02716     }
02717     else {
02718         switch (ptype) {
02719             case PROP_BOOLEAN:
02720             case PROP_INT:
02721             case PROP_ENUM:
02722                 return sizeof(int);
02723             case PROP_FLOAT:
02724                 return sizeof(float);
02725             case PROP_STRING:
02726                 /* return values don't store a pointer to the original */
02727                 if (parm->flag & PROP_THICK_WRAP) {
02728                     StringPropertyRNA *sparm = (StringPropertyRNA*)parm;
02729                     return sizeof(char) * sparm->maxlength;
02730                 }
02731                 else
02732                     return sizeof(char *);
02733             case PROP_POINTER: {
02734 #ifdef RNA_RUNTIME
02735                 if (parm->flag & PROP_RNAPTR)
02736                     return sizeof(PointerRNA);
02737                 else
02738                     return sizeof(void *);
02739 #else
02740                 if (parm->flag & PROP_RNAPTR)
02741                     return sizeof(PointerRNA);
02742                 else
02743                     return sizeof(void *);
02744 #endif
02745             }
02746             case PROP_COLLECTION:
02747                 return sizeof(ListBase);
02748         }
02749     }
02750 
02751     return sizeof(void *);
02752 }
